title: Atlanta Rhythm Section-1997-So into you
description:
This is a recording from 1997, where ARS revisited some of their best songs.

It&#039;s a heavier sound, a little slower and a little bit "over the hill".

But what&#039;s that to hard core fans?

The line-up:
Ronnie Hammond, vocals
Barry Bailey, lead guitar
Dean Daughtry, keyboards
Steve Stone, guitar
Justin Senker, bass
R.J. Vealey, drums
